Signup test cases:


1. Sign up using a valid email

2. Sign up while leaving email field empty

3. Sign up while leaving password field empty

4. Sign up while having password different from confirm password

5. Sign up while leaving repassword field empty

6. Verify shown password and confirmed password

7. Verify navigating to login page from sign up page

8. Verify using a invalid format of email

9. Verify signing up with easy to guess password

10. Verify signing up with short password
